  "detailed_description": "You suddenly enter a whole new world empty-handed. Start a whole new adventure all your own. Farming, fishing, building, cooking, alchemy and living a quiet life. Or is it fighting monsters, leveling up, learning skills, building equipment and discovering the hidden secrets of the world? Or maybe I want them all.<br>Find magic stones, money, and other useful things, craft tools, craft weapons, and gather the resources you need to create everything.<br>Build a house, a fort, even a castle. Invite people to move in and they'll offer portable features or sell items to help you complete your journey! Or even go on a journey with you!<br>In this game, you can build your own hut to defend against external threats!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/cb68ff3adb4fb98534790a6d3fd02939.avif?t=1770629356\" width=770 height=588 /></span><br><br>Of course, you can also build empty huts to invite NPCS to move in and they will provide you with all kinds of help!<br>Want to get rich first farm! You can grow a variety of fruits and vegetables and use them for cooking or alchemy or give them to NPCS! But don't forget to water it every day<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/b3f7e5e475e50754f1c489f6767f3e5e.avif?t=1770629356\" width=658 height=554 /></span><br><br>Or enjoy leisurely but unknown fishing<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/1cb968b78f94e067a074cd7e7fa861c8.avif?t=1770629356\" width=386 height=170 /></span><br><br>Dig into all kinds of resources to create the weapons, armor, tools, building accessories you want!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/0a00bb93fc0d0ac8f921305be9232e65.avif?t=1770629356\" width=709 height=491 /></span><br><br>Kill monsters raise your level and learn the skills you want!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/8c60e06335c8336dd81a083dfa552a3c.avif?t=1770629356\" width=397 height=213 /></span><br><br>Challenge the boss for more power!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/980c9c7d704f3ce766f9a28f626c6c94.poster.avif?t=1770629356\" width=500 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/980c9c7d704f3ce766f9a28f626c6c94.webm?t=1770629356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/980c9c7d704f3ce766f9a28f626c6c94.mp4?t=1770629356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use the alchemy table to explore unknown recipes and develop completely unknown potions!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/ce8aceba3d321bd0522f3ecd4d345d1a.avif?t=1770629356\" width=283 height=266 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "You suddenly enter a whole new world empty-handed. Start a whole new adventure all your own. Farming, fishing, building, cooking, alchemy and living a quiet life. Or is it fighting monsters, leveling up, learning skills, building equipment and discovering the hidden secrets of the world? Or maybe I want them all.<br>Find magic stones, money, and other useful things, craft tools, craft weapons, and gather the resources you need to create everything.<br>Build a house, a fort, even a castle. Invite people to move in and they'll offer portable features or sell items to help you complete your journey! Or even go on a journey with you!<br>In this game, you can build your own hut to defend against external threats!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/cb68ff3adb4fb98534790a6d3fd02939.avif?t=1770629356\" width=770 height=588 /></span><br><br>Of course, you can also build empty huts to invite NPCS to move in and they will provide you with all kinds of help!<br>Want to get rich first farm! You can grow a variety of fruits and vegetables and use them for cooking or alchemy or give them to NPCS! But don't forget to water it every day<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/b3f7e5e475e50754f1c489f6767f3e5e.avif?t=1770629356\" width=658 height=554 /></span><br><br>Or enjoy leisurely but unknown fishing<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/1cb968b78f94e067a074cd7e7fa861c8.avif?t=1770629356\" width=386 height=170 /></span><br><br>Dig into all kinds of resources to create the weapons, armor, tools, building accessories you want!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/0a00bb93fc0d0ac8f921305be9232e65.avif?t=1770629356\" width=709 height=491 /></span><br><br>Kill monsters raise your level and learn the skills you want!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/8c60e06335c8336dd81a083dfa552a3c.avif?t=1770629356\" width=397 height=213 /></span><br><br>Challenge the boss for more power!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/980c9c7d704f3ce766f9a28f626c6c94.poster.avif?t=1770629356\" width=500 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/980c9c7d704f3ce766f9a28f626c6c94.webm?t=1770629356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/980c9c7d704f3ce766f9a28f626c6c94.mp4?t=1770629356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use the alchemy table to explore unknown recipes and develop completely unknown potions!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865010/extras/ce8aceba3d321bd0522f3ecd4d345d1a.avif?t=1770629356\" width=283 height=266 /></span>",
